Class Program

java.lang.Object
  beans.Program
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Program
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class contains ways to program a movie into a complex. It also provides us a way to add a movie Afterwards , users can look at the programming list and choose the movie they want to see. All Information about the programming will be saved into the database.
